<br>
--------------------------------<br>
<br>
The silence was quite stunning after my speech.  I couldn't tell if I had stunned them with my eloquence or horrified them.  A couple of trying moments went by that were quite straining, my greatest fear was that my sweat would start showing through my shirt.<br>
<br>
Segal gestures and starts to speak as he is interrupted by a grizzled hard eyed veteran stands up and turns to me.<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Well now you young pup. You seem to have worked up what you may be thinking was all the right phrases and statements but you ducked and dodged all the important issues as iff'n you were a pansy Elf trapped in a food fight cross-fire!!!</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
The dread creeps over me as to what, only heaven knew if it was brave enough to look into that hardened mass called a brain, was going to jump forth from this codger's mouth.<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> I, myself, just want you to answer plainly and clearly you hear! And you better answer fast as if  yer mangy life depends upon it. It might!</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot; He squints as he looks me over. Then he barks out his question while pointing his gnarled finger at me. &quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> WHAT is your favorite color!!!!!</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
His arms cross in anticipation of my failed response. &quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Damn this old-timers,</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot; I think, &quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> They just hammer ya like unworked steel until they think they know your worth... and it takes forever for that to happen.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
Well I took in the gasps of anticipation as the room considers what confrontation may develop from this worthy's volley.<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Hmm, volley fire eh? Wonder what he'll do with my trusty machine gun lobs!!!</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
I squint my left eye, curl the left side of my face while uttering in a raspy voice, &quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Well here now old timer. I  can't rightfully decide which is best!</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
I notice a delightful look on his face but just before he can hammer me I continue.<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Yeller</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> bellied chickens can brighten a day jus' before I cut them down. Arh! The splash of <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Red</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> that gusher's from an Orc's neck was it's head goes down range is sometun' almost downright divine.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
As I am speaking I can see him considering the thoughts I'm expressing.<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Now I truly can't decide whether it's the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> blue</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> of the intestines or the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> green</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> from the bile that's best after slicin' open someones gizzard and spillin' his guts.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> The <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> white</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> palor of of a brigand's face as he knows the his doom is upon him is can be quite lively.  And I can't tell you how many hours I have sat contemplating the fullness of color from dangling <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> black</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> fruit that was once a pirate.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
Appreciation washes across this codger's face as Segal does a couple of quiet swallows to settle his stomach. &quot;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Hmmmm, quite a few doing that here,</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot; as I recompose myself for the next round of questioning. <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> OOC: That there hopscotch dance answer and not answer yer question matie?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
